videos.description: Ryan McMahon gets the inbounds pass and throws up a heave at the buzzer that goes in, but is waived off with no time on the clock.

videos.description: Off the loose ball, Jordan Usher drives in for the one-handed jam and proceeds to mean mug.

videos.headline: Louisville inching closer on McMahon's 3
